\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces LLM Proxy Router architecture: the router operates between the requesting client and the model population. The \textit  {Purpose Layer}\ layer sets routing weights; the \textit  {Bounds Engine}\ engine computes per-model scores; the \textit  {Fact Layer}\ layer enforces compliance filters before selection. The Model Capability Registry provides live state to the \textit  {Bounds Engine}\ engine.}}{2}{figure.1}\protected@file@percent }
